nt, Gloria revealing a victorious, loving smile.\nThe \"Glorious Deliverance Agency (GDA1)\" is thus established. For that illusory resonance packaged as a \"cosmic miracle\" through manipulation, the protagonist has personally pushed themselves into a bottomless abyss called \"toxic positivity.\"\n[Pages 1-10 Complete, Act I: The Fatal Honeymoon Ends]",
