	},
	{
		"title_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_27_TITLE",
		"title_en": "Page 27",
		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_27_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Visual: Something even more absurd happens. To prevent One without a microphone from understanding their 'perfect plan,' ARK actually starts loudly issuing commands in broken German.\nARK (shouting into microphone, deliberately showing off): 'Das war ein Befehl! Ich habe das 2024 gemacht! (This is an order! I did it this way in 2024!)'\nThough the protagonist can understand German from studying abroad, One cannot. Outside their three-person circle, One, without a radio and unable to understand this conversation, stands awkwardly in the muddy water like a transparent person, at a loss.",
