		"title_en": "Page 28",
		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_28_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Visual: One tries to step closer to hear what they're planning, but ARK deliberately turns around, using his wide back to block him. One's eyes dim, silently retreating to his original position.\nProtagonist (pulling ARK aside, roaring): 'What the hell are you doing?! We're a team! One can't understand your damn language, you won't even share microphones with us! You won't even disclose the plan, are you deliberately excluding him?!'\nARK (spreading hands, expression of 'you're making a big fuss'): 'Relax, no worries! I'm improving efficiency. I've already decided the direction, you just need to follow. What's there to worry about?'",
