		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_30_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Scene: Deep in scrapyard, before a radiation obstacle.\nVisual: A huge acid-rain-corroded heavy metal blast door blocks the way. Someone must move it bare-handed. This is extremely exhausting dirty work with radiation burn risk.\nProtagonist (looking at aluminum-can-armored Donkey): 'Your turn. You said you're a knight? Move it.'\nDonkey (walking to the blast door, pretending to gesture, suddenly clutching his forehead with an extremely exaggerated pained expression): 'Ah! This evil aura... wait! My keen hero radar senses it! In the southeast of the scrapyard, a pure princess is being besieged by mutant rat swarms! She's calling my name!'",
