		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_32_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Visual: No one chases Donkey. ARK even starts humming a tune.\nOnly One. He silently walks to the dangerously glowing blast door, wordlessly bends down, and with bare hands without any protection, firmly grips the rusty edge, using all his strength to lift. Sharp rust pierces his palms, blood mixed with muddy water dripping.\nGloria (watching this scene, not helping, instead clasping hands and closing eyes to pray): 'Great FSM, please grant Donkey the power to rescue the princess, and please bless our current obstacle to be smoothly removed...'\nVisual ([Positive Energy Curse Triggered]): Just as Gloria devoutly prays, a rusty iron frame above the scrapyard that was already precariously hanging suddenly emits a harsh breaking sound due to some inexplicable physical decay, crashing down with a 'boom,' nearly hitting One who's moving the door!\n(The prayer didn't bring miracles, but instead accelerated the collapse of the surrounding environment.)",
