	},
	{
		"title_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_33_TITLE",
		"title_en": "Page 33",
		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_33_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Protagonist (tackling One to dodge the iron frame, eyes reddening with fury): 'Enough!! Is this your so-called team?! Ark, your plan is a complete black box joke! You only say 'No worries' while watching teammates walk to their deaths! And Donkey, that deserter with a head full of feudal garbage, throwing all the most dangerous work to One!'\nVisual: The protagonist suddenly stands, pressing close to Gloria.\nProtagonist: 'And you! Don't you see that the more you pray, the faster this godforsaken place collapses?! This ship is sinking. Your blindness and shirking responsibility will get us all killed!'",
