		"title_en": "Page 37",
		"text_zh": "INTRO_DATA_PAGE_37_TEXT",
		"text_en": "Scene: Evening at the 'Greenhouse' shelter.\nVisual: After the scrapyard turmoil, the squad returns to camp. Donkey, who deserted in the face of battle, is already sitting in the greenhouse, holding a withered rose, boasting to Gloria about his false achievements.\nBut this time, the protagonist isn't angry. They sit quietly in the corner, eyes having lost their former sharpness, replaced by a post-brainwashing fervor and humility.\nGloria (turning the fire-hazard Life Bread lampshade to maximum brightness, face glowing with fanatical happiness): 'Dear family, today we experienced trials, but the universe's frequency has bound us tightly together again! Now, we will officially establish eternal team bonds witnessed by FSM!'",
